body:
## Problem
Four high-priority pages in `api/sitemap.js` have **no dedicated handler** in `api/meta/[...path].js`, so crawlers receive the generic fallback title `MetalForge — Metal Drummer Gear Database`.

| Path | Sitemap priority | Changefreq |
|------|-----------------|------------|
| `/battles` | 0.9 | weekly |
| `/quotes` | 0.9 | weekly |
| `/endorsement-news` | 0.9 | weekly |
| `/facts` | 0.8 | monthly |

Verified in code: `grep -n "battles\|/quotes\|endorsement-news\|/facts" api/meta/[...path].js` → zero results for these paths. All fall to the default fallback at line ~925.

**Same bug class as:** #1300 (/gear hub), #1299 (/history), #1348 (/vs hub), #1349 (/guides hub) — all approved/shipped.

## Fix
**File:** `api/meta/[...path].js` — add 4 matchers after the `/history` handler (line ~925):

```javascript
// Drummer Battles page
if (path === '/battles') {
  return {
    title: `Metal Drummer Battles — Vote for the Best | ${SITE_NAME}`,
    description: 'Vote in head-to-head metal drummer battles. Who has the better kit? Compare setups and cast your vote for 60+ legendary drummers.',
    image: DEFAULT_IMAGE,
    type: 'website',
    url: `${BASE_URL}/battles`,
  };
}

// Drummer Quotes page
if (path === '/quotes') {
  return {
    title: `Metal Drummer Quotes — Insights on Gear & Technique | ${SITE_NAME}`,
    description: "Memorable quotes from the world's greatest metal drummers on gear, technique, and the craft. From Lars Ulrich, Joey Jordison, Tomas Haake, and 60+ legends.",
    image: DEFAULT_IMAGE,
    type: 'website',
    url: `${BASE_URL}/quotes`,
  };
}

// Endorsement News page
if (path === '/endorsement-news') {
  return {
    title: `Metal Drummer Endorsement News — Brand Deals & Sponsorships | ${SITE_NAME}`,
    description: 'Latest endorsement deals and brand sponsorships in metal drumming. Track which drum brands are signing which metal drummers.',
    image: DEFAULT_IMAGE,
    type: 'website',
    url: `${BASE_URL}/endorsement-news`,
  };
}

// Quick Facts page
if (path === '/facts') {
  return {
    title: `Metal Drummer Quick Facts — Records, Stats & Trivia | ${SITE_NAME}`,
    description: 'Quick facts, records, and trivia about metal drummers. Fastest blast beats, most expensive kits, career milestones, and gear stats from 60+ pros.',
    image: DEFAULT_IMAGE,
    type: 'website',
    url: `${BASE_URL}/facts`,
  };
}
```

## Estimated organic uplift
4 hub pages at sitemap priority 0.9/0.8 gain keyword-matched SERP snippets. Serves navigational + branded queries. Enables Google to understand page purpose on first-pass crawl.

## Verify
1. `curl -s -A 'Googlebot' 'https://metalforge.io/api/meta/battles'` → title contains "Battle"
2. `curl -s -A 'Googlebot' 'https://metalforge.io/api/meta/quotes'` → title contains "Quotes"
3. `curl -s -A 'Googlebot' 'https://metalforge.io/api/meta/endorsement-news'` → title contains "Endorsement"
4. `curl -s -A 'Googlebot' 'https://metalforge.io/api/meta/facts'` → title contains "Facts"
5. None return the generic fallback title `MetalForge — Metal Drummer Gear Database`

## Done
All 4 paths return keyword-matched title/description from `api/meta/[...path].js`.
